a <- 1:5
tbl <- tibble::tibble(a, b = a * 2, c = 1)
suppressMessages({
  devtools::load_all()
})
sureplot(
  {
    plot(tbl$a, tbl$b, xlab = "foo")
  },
  height = 4,
  par_opts = list(bg = "azure")
)
